      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二月二十七日　朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1466.6664838999998,
          "startTime": 2.2666664839
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1499.9998171999998,
          "startTime": 2.2999998172
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.6666666,
          "startTime": 5.0666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございまーす！\nあ、いたいた優ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようさん。すみれちゃん、えらい早いなぁ\nレッスンまでまだまだ時間あるけど、どないしたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4666668892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんなら早入りして自主練してるかと思って！\nあのね、今日は優ちゃんに渡したいものがあるの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7400.000000000002,
          "startTime": 26.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "お誕生日おめでとうございます！\nほら、開けてみて開けてみて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2600.0000397999975,
          "startTime": 29.4000000398
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "わあ、おおきに～！\nなんやろなあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、けん玉や！　こんなん絶対ええやつやん\nほら、木目のところがすっごい綺麗な――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "お分かりになりますかっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6333356619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "……はい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3333321015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "けんはブナ！　玉はサクラ！　厳選された木材を\n本場山形の職人が手ずから削って組み上げた逸品！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6808472077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "見てみ～、ほら大皿小皿が描く魅力の曲線美を！\n例えたらこれは万物を優しく抱き留める山形の聖杯！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、磨き抜かれた工芸品の、何と美しいことやろか！\nほらほら見てみぃ、この計算され尽くしたフォルム！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "なんなんその口調！？\nま、まぁ、確かに凄い綺麗やけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "それだけちゃうで！　端から端までまんべんなく\n仕込まれた匠の技……！　手に馴染んで離さへん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "これこそまさしく「けん玉」！！\nいや、けん玉の中のけん玉っちゅうても過言やない！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっと…………せやから、すみれちゃん\nなんなんって、その口調？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、好きなものを語ってる時の優ちゃんを\nちょっとマネしてみたの。どう？　似てたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、全然似てへんやん！　……とは言い切れない\nうちってほんまにこんな風に見えてんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、優ちゃんはもっとこう、ハスハスしてるかも？\n頭からリテイクお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、もう、これ以上はもう、堪忍してぇな……\nうわぁ、うちあんなんなんか……気ぃつけよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "私、好きなものを楽しそうに話す優ちゃんが大好きなの\nだから私も優ちゃんに語ってみたいなって思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yuu Suzumura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "なんや……そういうことやったんや\nそれやったら、せっかくやし……教えてもらおかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_53_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　任せて！\n優ちゃんをけん玉の達人にしちゃうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5,
      "sfxList": [
